{
  "stem": "21582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I think it's because they bring back very pleasant memories.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They kind of give me an illusion of security and yet not isolation because you could look right through them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I loved the clanging of the-- of the gates when they were closed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Beyond-- beyond-- behind the gate was a large, rectangular courtyard in the-- which was surrounded by four buildings that stood at right angles to one another.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And in the center was a little garden, a fenced-in garden.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the rest of the yard-- of the courtyard was paved.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that's where the children played, under the windows where they could not escape the supervision of their parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Generally, our streets were very safe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I remember with enormous fondness our holidays and, and the warmth and security of the community, friendly neighbors, holidays when we would gather together, play with cousins and friends and hear conversations of adults.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they were all wonderful memories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] However, outside my immediate neighborhood-- we lived in a Jewish section of town-- outside my immediate neighborhood, when I reflect on it, I-- and mixed feelings come back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Every-- not every Saturday, but very often, my-- we would go to the park for a walk.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Now, I-- Warsaw was a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was my city.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was my home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It was my center.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was all I knew, and I loved it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "That's all I knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I loved the parks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Yet I remember that in my parks, when I would go for a walk with my parents, suddenly, there would be an outbreak of panic.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And you would see people just running.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And you would hear this, this wild laughter of pursuers.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
